-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fixed a bug related to calculating space for the column and row names. Made the
documentation more readable

Added .Rbuildignore

Version 0.7.6
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fixed a bug, where the color scales for scaled matrices were not centered to 0.

